    "verzending_cards": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>.sw-vz-cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1.5rem}@media(min-width:640px){.sw-vz-cards{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}</style><div style=\"background:#f9fafb;padding:3rem 0\"><div style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem\"><div class=\"sw-vz-cards\"><div style=\"background:#fff;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.75rem;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);border:1px solid #f0f0f0\"><div style=\"width:3rem;height:3rem;border-radius:50%;background:#EBF2FF;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1rem\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"1\" y=\"3\" width=\"15\" height=\"13\"/><polygon points=\"16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8\"/><circle cx=\"5.5\" cy=\"18.5\" r=\"2.5\"/><circle cx=\"18.5\" cy=\"18.5\" r=\"2.5\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-weight:700;color:#111827;font-size:1.0625rem;margin:0 0 .75rem\">Bezorging</h3><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.5rem\"><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Gratis bezorging bij bestellingen &euro;50+</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Voor 22:00 besteld = morgen in huis</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Bezorging via PostNL of DHL</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Track &amp; trace per e-mail</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#fff;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.75rem;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);border:1px solid #f0f0f0\"><div style=\"width:3rem;height:3rem;border-radius:50%;background:#EBF2FF;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1rem\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"1 4 1 10 7 10\"/><path d=\"M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 0 .49-4.47\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-weight:700;color:#111827;font-size:1.0625rem;margin:0 0 .75rem\">Retourneren</h3><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.5rem\"><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>30 dagen retourrecht</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Gratis retourzending</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Geld terug binnen 5 werkdagen</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Originele verpakking niet vereist</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#fff;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.75rem;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);border:1px solid #f0f0f0\"><div style=\"width:3rem;height:3rem;border-radius:50%;background:#EBF2FF;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1rem\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-weight:700;color:#111827;font-size:1.0625rem;margin:0 0 .75rem\">Garantie</h3><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.5rem\"><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>2 jaar garantie op alle producten</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Defect? Wij lossen het op</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Snel en eenvoudig aanvragen</li><li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.5rem;font-size:.9rem;color:#4b5563\"><span style=\"color:#0F6FE3;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0\">&#10003;</span>Geen gedoe, gewoon geregeld</li></ul></div></div></div></div>",
