    "verzending_detail": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>.sw-vz-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2.5rem}@media(min-width:1024px){.sw-vz-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}</style><section style=\"padding:4rem 0;background:#fff\"><div style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem\"><div class=\"sw-vz-layout\"><div><h2 style=\"font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin:0 0 1.5rem;padding-bottom:.75rem;border-bottom:2px solid #EBF2FF\">Verzendkosten &amp; levertijden</h2><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem\"><div style=\"background:#f9fafb;border-radius:.75rem;padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid #e5e7eb\"><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem\"><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:#111827\">Bestelling onder &euro;50</span><span style=\"background:#0F6FE3;color:#fff;padding:.2rem .75rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.8125rem;font-weight:600\">&euro;4,95</span></div><p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:.875rem;margin:.375rem 0 0\">Bezorging via PostNL of DHL, 1&ndash;2 werkdagen</p></div><div style=\"background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:.75rem;padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid #86efac\"><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem\"><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:#111827\">Bestelling boven &euro;50</span><span style=\"background:#16a34a;color:#fff;padding:.2rem .75rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.8125rem;font-weight:600\">GRATIS</span></div><p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:.875rem;margin:.375rem 0 0\">Gratis bezorging, volgende werkdag</p></div><div style=\"background:#f9fafb;border-radius:.75rem;padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid #e5e7eb\"><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem\"><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:#111827\">Bestelling voor 22:00</span><span style=\"background:#083D7D;color:#fff;padding:.2rem .75rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.8125rem;font-weight:600\">Morgen in huis</span></div><p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:.875rem;margin:.375rem 0 0\">Op werkdagen (ma&ndash;vr). Uitgezonderd feestdagen.</p></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:2rem;background:#EBF2FF;border-radius:.75rem;padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid #bfdbfe\"><p style=\"color:#083D7D;font-size:.875rem;margin:0\"><strong>&#9432; Let op:</strong> Bezorging vindt plaats op werkdagen. Bestellingen geplaatst in het weekend worden maandag verwerkt.</p></div></div><div><h2 style=\"font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin:0 0 1.5rem;padding-bottom:.75rem;border-bottom:2px solid #EBF2FF\">Retourinstructies</h2><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem\"><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem\"><div style=\"width:2rem;height:2rem;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#083D7D,#0F6FE3);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:.875rem;flex-shrink:0\">1</div><div><h4 style=\"font-weight:700;color:#111827;font-size:.9375rem;margin:0 0 .25rem\">Neem contact op</h4><p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:.875rem;margin:0\">Mail naar info@spotwereld.nl of bel ons. Vermeld je ordernummer.</p></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem\"><div style=\"width:2rem;height:2rem;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#083D7D,#0F6FE3);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:.875rem;flex-shrink:0\">2</div><div><h4 style=\"font-weight:700;color:#111827;font-size:.9375rem;margin:0 0 .25rem\">Ontvang retourlabel</h4><p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:.875rem;margin:0\">Wij sturen je een gratis retourlabel per e-mail.</p></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem\"><div style=\"width:2rem;height:2rem;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#083D7D,#0F6FE3);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:.875rem;flex-shrink:0\">3</div><div><h4 style=\"font-weight:700;color:#111827;font-size:.9375rem;margin:0 0 .25rem\">Stuur het pakket terug</h4><p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:.875rem;margin:0\">Verpak het product goed en lever het in bij een PostNL punt.</p></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem\"><div style=\"width:2rem;height:2rem;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#083D7D,#0F6FE3);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:.875rem;flex-shrink:0\">4</div><div><h4 style=\"font-weight:700;color:#111827;font-size:.9375rem;margin:0 0 .25rem\">Geld terug</h4><p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:.875rem;margin:0\">Na ontvangst en controle, geld terug binnen 5 werkdagen.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:2rem;padding:1.25rem;background:#fff7ed;border-radius:.75rem;border:1px solid #fdba74\"><p style=\"color:#9a3412;font-size:.875rem;margin:0\"><strong>Voorwaarden:</strong> Product mag niet gebruikt zijn. Retourneren kan tot 30 dagen na ontvangst. Bij beschadiging door onzorgvuldig gebruik geldt geen garantie.</p></div></div></div></div></section>",
